data.description:
GORGEOUS villa in the highly desired community of Villa San Remo. This spacious 2 bedroom/2 bathroom welcomes you home with its bright and light updates boasting porcelain tiles throughout the living area and modernized interior lighting.  The kitchen showcases  granite countertops and all new stainless steel appliances located directly across from the dining area.  The ample sized primary bedroom opens up to the screened in patio through sliding glass doors and contains its own en-suite bathroom.  Access to the screened patio can also be found through the living room.  Additional features include lush landscaping, 2020 roof, fresh exterior paint, 2021 AC unit, epoxy flooring in the garage, generator hook-up, and electric roll down hurricane shutters. Resort pool, jacuzzi, sauna, clubhouse, tennis & fitness center are all in walking distance from your front door.
Villa San Remo has manned gated security & zoned for Boca's A RATED SCHOOLS. Association covers the roof, cable, internet, insurance, common areas & lawn. You can rent this property after 2 years of ownership.
